text: Rolf Kühn (29 September 1929 – 18 August 2022) was a German jazz clarinetist and saxophonist. He was the older brother of the pianist Joachim Kühn. He was called the "German Benny Goodman". ==References== Category:1929 births Category:2022 deaths Category:German jazz musicians Category:Clarinetists Category:Saxophonists Category:People from Cologne
